{"tid":359013,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"辣妹胸罩沒扣好　害大家都忘了安全帽","createTime":"2017-08-14T06:56:12.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-16T10:15:09.000Z","uid":55981,"like":1,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2aa4c3d563072684db590c6af94138f1a461be4a","tid":359013,"uid":55981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T06:56:12.000Z","msg":"2017年08月14日11:32      <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20170814/640_560b52b1f354f5b760690bfbd068a3ac.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20170814%2F640_560b52b1f354f5b760690bfbd068a3ac.jpg&h=d97549c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n事情是這樣的...<br />\n<br />\n網友在臉書社團爆廢公社分享街景，意外發現一名身穿薄紗的女機車騎士「胸罩沒有扣好」！<br />\n<br />\n這下所有人都要把她當路隊長了（誤），卻有眼尖網友發現，重點是前面那輛機車，騎士沒戴安全帽吧...<br />\n<br />\n「警察先生會因為你沒戴安全帽而開罰單，可不會因為你沒穿好內衣而開罰單吧！」（即時新聞中心／綜合報導）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/new/20170814/1181822/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.appledaily.com.tw%2Frealtimenews%2Farticle%2Fnew%2F20170814%2F1181822%2F&d=2%2FWHG351XZVBiXPaDmUC%2Fp4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=eee52d51\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/new/20170814/1181822/</a>"},{"pid":"0af115c23731b7ddc0b3a668e82cc62a29d59aa2","tid":359013,"uid":110832,"like":33,"dislike":1,"score":32,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T06:58:46.000Z","msg":"屌你老母台灣記者真係好做<br />\n<br />\n呢啲係放係fb 19 page嘅野都拎黎報"},{"pid":"d0b119e678f0e2120fde9780674199fef9e20ca7","tid":359013,"uid":41695,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T07:01:30.000Z","msg":"咁都上新聞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac2da81c41ad3a8a964546bedde909abd4090228","tid":359013,"uid":5490,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T07:03:04.000Z","msg":"馬總統"},{"pid":"bad8937760ca1b8ff9301b877ffeac5965ef623e","tid":359013,"uid":69753,"li